优势。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-57b715dc7f0cec0f1e89a1a46ccfdfbe_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "320 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/492109817"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4Pq8lq/o8Pd5EAMaCDcxNjM5MTgwIOCWmYsGMAA4bkAHcgk0OTIxMDk4MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1634178169.4704227", "card_id": "Q_472892637", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 97}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在的网文新书名字这么奇奇怪怪又臭又长？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ea6d325fe02e6df995a880ea44df66fb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "315 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/472892637"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4Pq8lq/o8Pd5EAMaCDY3MzY2ODQxIO2fzIcGMAw4jwJACHIJNDcyODkyNjM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1634178169.4708965", "card_id": "Q_492098947", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1169}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待男子举鲤鱼旗带团参观中山陵， 游客提醒反被驳「中国传到日本去的」？旅游行业应如何规范导游行为？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据 @星视频 消息，网友爆料一男子举鲤鱼旗带学生参观中山陵。一名女子上前提醒让其不要使用此旗被男子反驳。男子称这是锦鲤旗，是中国传到日本去的。随后被旁边游客拉开。鲤鱼旗，在日本为庆祝五月五日男孩节，家有男孩的，家家挂鲤鱼旗。此风俗始于江户时代，原是农历端午节的风俗。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-43ca6510a6d77e41fd06bec02a530df6_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "281 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/492098947"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI4Pq8lq/o8Pd5EAMaCDcxNjM2Nzc0INuEmYsGMJ8COM8YQAlyCTQ5MjA5ODk0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1634178169.4716058", "card_id": "Q_476474620", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 176}, 